  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/a3e015c50ab0f8b1443c47c7c0dc2692.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blagmoz</strong> pits you and up to three friends head-to-head in  spell-slinging combat where only the craftiest sorcerers come out on top. Master tight movement mechanics and use every resource available to claw your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/84b49d2744a02a72c616e3634876a161.poster.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/84b49d2744a02a72c616e3634876a161.webm?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/84b49d2744a02a72c616e3634876a161.mp4?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Think Fast Under Pressure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift the tides of battle by taking out the most powerful wizard and absorbing their essence at the Altar, or grab some potions that give access to new movement options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/ce26448ad0307fed77927485c56087ed.poster.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/ce26448ad0307fed77927485c56087ed.webm?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/ce26448ad0307fed77927485c56087ed.mp4?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle on the Couch or Online</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play locally or host an online match for your friends. But who needs friends anyway, because Blagmoz has a public server browser, too! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/774925d0fc9cc78f9b66aeec8842b2d6.poster.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/774925d0fc9cc78f9b66aeec8842b2d6.webm?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/774925d0fc9cc78f9b66aeec8842b2d6.mp4?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-4 player online or local multiplayer + a public lobby browser </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level editor and Steam Workshop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable game modifiers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80+ levels across 3 worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 18 potions that buff you up, hinder your opponents, and turn people into frogs </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious rising sea of goo </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wall jumping, wave dashing, and head stomping action </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable worlds, potions, and costumes </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/d3cd966bc11bcdf3b3b2a7b878660f77.poster.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/d3cd966bc11bcdf3b3b2a7b878660f77.webm?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/d3cd966bc11bcdf3b3b2a7b878660f77.mp4?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/a3e015c50ab0f8b1443c47c7c0dc2692.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blagmoz</strong> pits you and up to three friends head-to-head in  spell-slinging combat where only the craftiest sorcerers come out on top. Master tight movement mechanics and use every resource available to claw your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/84b49d2744a02a72c616e3634876a161.poster.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/84b49d2744a02a72c616e3634876a161.webm?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/84b49d2744a02a72c616e3634876a161.mp4?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Think Fast Under Pressure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shift the tides of battle by taking out the most powerful wizard and absorbing their essence at the Altar, or grab some potions that give access to new movement options.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/ce26448ad0307fed77927485c56087ed.poster.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/ce26448ad0307fed77927485c56087ed.webm?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/ce26448ad0307fed77927485c56087ed.mp4?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle on the Couch or Online</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play locally or host an online match for your friends. But who needs friends anyway, because Blagmoz has a public server browser, too! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/774925d0fc9cc78f9b66aeec8842b2d6.poster.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/774925d0fc9cc78f9b66aeec8842b2d6.webm?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/774925d0fc9cc78f9b66aeec8842b2d6.mp4?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-4 player online or local multiplayer + a public lobby browser </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level editor and Steam Workshop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customizable game modifiers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >80+ levels across 3 worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 18 potions that buff you up, hinder your opponents, and turn people into frogs </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mysterious rising sea of goo </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wall jumping, wave dashing, and head stomping action </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlockable worlds, potions, and costumes </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/d3cd966bc11bcdf3b3b2a7b878660f77.poster.avif?t=1771392672\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/d3cd966bc11bcdf3b3b2a7b878660f77.webm?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614970/extras/d3cd966bc11bcdf3b3b2a7b878660f77.mp4?t=1771392672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
